name: Rusty Fuzz
details:
Silicon-Based Fuzz with Vintage Gated and Velcro-Like TonesRUSTY FUZZ delivers those vintage silicon-based fuzz tones of yesteryear that we’ve all come to know and love, but at a price point so low everyone can play along. From silky-smooth sustain to ripping velcro-fuzz tones, RUSTY FUZZ does it all! So whether you’re experienced or not (See what we did there?), this compact true bypass pedal is sure to cover your old-school Fuzz Face craving.
